<book2> <http://example.org/ont/price> 15 .
<http://example.org/book3> ont:price 25 .
<book4> ont:price 12 .
<http://example.org/book4> <http://example.org/ont/name> "Book 4" .
<http://example.org/book5> <http://example.org/ont/price> "null" .
<http://example.org/book5> <http://example.org/ont/pageCount> 500 .